text:
──Ah! Natsuha, sorry...
The last train is coming soon, so I should head out.

Oh, is it that late already?
I wanted to practice more, what a shame.

Oh, that's right.
Why don't you stay over, Juri?

Eh? No... but it's sudden, and...
you know... I'd feel bad.

Oh, are you worried about that?
There's no one else here, so it's no problem at all.

The other day when it rained, you shared your umbrella
with me, didn't you? Think of it as my way of saying thank you.

............Alright.
Then... I'll take you up on that offer.

Hehe, it's settled!
Now we can continue where we left off.
